# FitLife UI Redesign — Walkthrough

## Overview

Complete UI redesign of the FitLife fitness application, inspired by the Fittr app's aesthetic. The redesign introduces a vibrant orange color scheme, dark mode base (Zinc-950), glassmorphism effects, Inter typography, and animated micro-interactions across all screens.

## What Changed

### Design Foundations

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| [index.css](file:///c:/Users/Kelly/OneDrive/Desktop/projects/fitlife/apps/web/src/index.css) | New CSS variables: vibrant orange `--primary`, Zinc-950 dark background, subtle border colors, `glass` and `animate-pulse-glow` utilities |
| [tailwind.config.js](file:///c:/Users/Kelly/OneDrive/Desktop/projects/fitlife/apps/web/tailwind.config.js) | Added `brand-orange`, `pulse-glow` animation keyframes, extended color palette |

