Feature Walkthrough
Per-User Data Isolation (Latest Fix)
Problem: All Zustand stores used fixed localStorage keys, so switching accounts showed the previous user's workouts, nutrition, goals, and schedule.

Fix: Added 
resetStore()
 to each data store and wired them into 
AuthSync.tsx
.

Store	Change
useWorkoutStore.ts
resetStore()
 clears activeSession + history
useScheduleStore.ts
resetStore()
 clears schedule
useNutritionStore.ts
resetStore()
 clears meals + waterCups
useGoalStore.ts
resetStore()
 resets to default starter goals
AuthSync
 now calls all reset functions on both logout (uid → null) and user switch (uid changed).

